<div class='media__message'>
<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>맥클릿 하데로(Meklit Hadero)</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/meklit_hadero_the_unexpected_beauty_of_everyday_sounds?language=ko' lang='ko'>
아름다운 일상의 소리
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Oct 2015
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Beautiful, Inspiring
</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
